>ℝ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">10</span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"bp\">ℕ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">*</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">*</span> <span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"o\">),</span> <span class=\"k\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">norm_num</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">generalize_hyp</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"mi\">10</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"n\">at</span> <span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">simp</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">myFunc</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">multiset</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">repeat</span><span class=\"o\">],</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">end</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
